---
source: tests/cli_json.rs
expression: normalize_help(&output.stdout)
---
Upload and download GigaFile public web files

Usage: rgfile [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  download     Download a file from a public GigaFile page [aliases: dl]
  info         Show metadata for a public GigaFile page without downloading files
  upload       Upload a local file [aliases: ul]
  delete       Delete an uploaded file using its delete key
  parts        List or clean leftover partial downloads
  history      Inspect or clear local history
  config       Inspect or create the rgfile configuration file
  self-update  Update this rgfile binary from the latest GitHub Release
  completions  Generate shell completion scripts
  help         Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version

Global Options:
  -v, --verbose...     Increase logging verbosity (-v for info, -vv for debug)
      --config <PATH>  Load configuration from a specific TOML file
      --no-config      Do not load a configuration file
      --history        Enable history for this run
      --no-history     Disable history for this run
